snippet.title: Djinn - The Forbidden Knowledge - Teaser
snippet.description:
#djinn #horror #videogame 

Haunted by a desperate past, you awaken to a terrifying new reality: a desolate and dark realm that echoes with your past. Now you must embrace the unknown and embark on an adventure to unveil its secrets. Are you ready to face your worst fears and emerge even stronger?

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2941750/Djinn__The_Forbidden_Knowledge

Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/djinn-the-forbidden-knowledge-1f5924

Music: Arabian Chase by Erik Margolin
